Routes
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
- /register -> Register user/driver
- /login -> Login user
- /search/orders  -> Get order info
- /search/stores -> Get Store info
- /store -> Create/Update store
- /order -> Create/Update order
- /user  -> Create/Update user







Classes
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
User
	- first name
	- last name
	- phone number
	- location
	- password

Driver inherits User
	- photo
	- license plate

Store
	- Menu
	- Driver(s)

Menu
	- Item(s)

Item
	- name
	- price
	- image

Order
	- Item(s)
	- Store
	- User
	- status	



